New Italian Book: Io & Charlie

   15 Jul 2019

   Orecchio Acerbo Editore has just published a lovely new children’s book
   entitled “Io e Charlie” (Charlie and Me) by Luca Tortolini with
   illustrations by Giacomo Garelli (licensed by Bubbles Inc. SA).
